    {
      "title": "",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 56 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Drill into test failures\n\nDetailed test-level pass rates, top failing tests, failure messages, and suite duration trends are in the **openshift-ci-observability** stack:\n\n- [CI Tests Dashboard →](/d/ci-tests) — Top failing tests, pass rates, slowest tests, JUnit failure messages\n- [CI Investigation →](/d/ci-investigation) — Per-PR failure analysis, build history, step errors\n- [CI Logs →](/d/ci-logs) — Raw ci-operator and step logs filtered by PR/build"
      }
    }
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["eng-metrics", "opendatahub", "ci"],
